          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1657033747758-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the rice is cooking, deseed your <strong>pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>pepper strips</strong> to the pan with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 5-6 min or until slightly softened</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
